      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine runs but exhibits a loud knocking sound and heavy exhaust smoke, indicating internal damage. Additionally, the transmission shifts harshly, and the interior shows heavy wear with several torn seats and broken trim pieces. This is an ideal candidate for a complete restoration project or for someone looking for a donor vehicle for parts.",
